nce or device&mdash;<br />\n&ldquo;(A) to intentionally kill the unborn child of a woman known to be pregnant; or<br />\n&ldquo;(B) to intentionally terminate the pregnancy of a woman known to be pregnant, with an intention other than&mdash;<br />\n&ldquo;(i) after viability, to produce a live birth and preserve the life and health of the child born alive; or<br />\n&ldquo;(ii) to remove a dead unborn child.<br />\n<br />\n即係 依家個胎有異常<br />\n要催產，預咗個嬰兒有機會夭折<br />\n醫護人員同家屬選擇<br />\n如果嬰兒無咩機會生存落去(not in survivable condition)<br />\n咁就唔會用盡一切手段去救佢<br />\n而係用類似舒緩治療嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n咁呢種「紓緩治療」<br />\n請問是否屬於草案中所講<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;(A) exercise the same degree of professional skill, care, and diligence to preserve the life and health of the child as a reasonably diligent and conscientious health care practitioner would render to any other child born alive at the same gestational age; and<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;(B) following the exercise of skill, care, and diligence required under subparagraph (A), ensure that the child born alive is immediately transported and admitted to a hospital.<br />\n<br />\n條草案嘅問題正正在於呢點不確定性"},{"pid":"963ddb500536076a8eae5850aa325a254129f187","tid":1047653,"uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4955315d1f1657b47c2c9f66cb0800a3f2813783","tid":1047653,"uid":38523,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"學某d連登仔講<br />\n其實共和黨都想否決個議案<br />\n但覺得有險可守先扮支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n@<br />\n一切是因果報應<br />\nHKVDC_2017<br />\n威猛的巨龍<br />\n等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"關我咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講民主黨<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（美國）</span></span>壞話即屌人既死忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f6103442321afecc6dc23c922d6b3d9bc4fb41","tid"